{{Infobox national volleyball team |name=Paraguay |image=Flag of Paraguay.svg |federation=Federación Paraguaya de Voleibol |website= |confederation=CSV |coach= |Olympic apps= |medaltemplates-expand=y |medaltemplates= {{MedalCompetition|[[South American Men's Volleyball Championship|South American Championship]]}} {{MedalBronze| 1979 | [[1979 Men's South American Volleyball Championship|Rosario]]}} {{MedalSilver| 1958 | [[1958 Men's South American Volleyball Championship|Porto Alegre]]}} {{MedalBronze| 1956 | [[1956 Men's South American Volleyball Championship|Montevideo]]}} }}
The '''Paraguay men's national volleyball team''' represents [[Paraguay]] in international [[volleyball]] competitions. In the 1950s the squad twice won a medal (silver and bronze) at the [[South American Men's Volleyball Championship|South American Championship]], and won another bronze medal in 1979 in Rosario, Argentina. Paraguay doesn't currently{{when|date=May 2017}} have a team, and does not participate in volleyball tournaments.
