{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Sokch Stadium | image = | location = [[Sokcho]], [[Gangwon-do (South Korea)|Gangwon-do]], [[South Korea]] | broke_ground = | opened = 1994 | owner = City of Sokcho | operator = City of Sokcho | surface = Natural grass | tenants = [[Gangwon FC]] (2015–present) | seating_capacity = 25,000 }}
'''Sokcho Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Sokcho]], [[South Korea]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium has a capacity for 25,000 spectators and was opened in 1994. <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.seoraknews.com/default/index_view_page.php?board_data=aWR4JTNEMTg5MDglMjZzdGFydFBhZ2UlM0QyMCUyNmxpc3RObyUzRDg1JTI2dG90YWxMaXN0JTNEMTE1%7C%7C&search_items=cGFydF9pZHglM0QxNTAlMjZ2aWV3X2NudCUzRCUyNmdyb3VwX2lkJTNEJTI2dmlld19wYWdlJTNE%7C%7C |title=속초종합운동장 리모델링 10일 완공 |language=Korean |publisher=Serak News|date=7 April 2014}}</ref>
It is home ground of [[Gangwon FC]] since 2015.
